1. Original : Jar of water 150 ml and oil 300 ml. What is the percent of water and oil?

Option 1 : What is the new percent of water and oil, when 50 ml of oil is added? 

Option 2: What is the new percent of water and oil, when 100 ml of water is added? 

Option 3: What is the new percent of water and oil, when 50 ml of oil and 50 ml of water is added?
